\id EPH Matupi Chin Standard Bible 
\h EPHESA 
\toc1 EPHESA 
\toc2 Ephesa 
\toc3 Eph 
\mt1 EPHESA  
\mt2 (Letter to the Ephesians)  
\is2 EPHESA CAPAT KAWNG  
\im Paul loh Ephesus Khrihca rhoek taengah ca a pat he a tha bahoeng om. Mamih loeih daemnah ham nih thinglam dongah Jesuh a duek (1.7,8). Tedae Pathen loh Khrih te dueknah khui lamkah a thoh sak. Te dongah Khrih loh diklai he a uk coeng. Hmailong ah khaw dungyan la a uk bal pueng ni (1.20,21).  
\ip Judah neh Gentile aka paekboe sak vongpuei te Khrih loh a phae tih Judah neh Gentiles tah pakhat la om coeng (2.14). Amih te Pathen Mueihla Cim a omnah Bawkim cim ah pakhat la a cului coeng (3.11).  
\ip Pilnam boeih kah a napa Pathen tah Boeipa Pakhat, Mueihla pakhat neh Pathen pakhat bueng ni a om (4.4,5). Mueihla loh thinko lungbuei pakhat la a khueh coeng atah Khrihca rhoek khaw thin at ko at la om saeh (4.3). Pum khat la omnah kawng he Ephesa capat dongah voei kul tluk a thui. Te dongah tangnah pakhat, baptistma pakhat long pum pakhat la n'coeng sak.  
\ip Ephesus he Asia Minor (Turkey) ram kah khotlak tupuei tungkaeng ah om. Paul tue vaengah tah Roman ram khuiah a pali nah khopuei len la om van. It Te vaengah amih kho ah te Artemis pathen nu muep a bawk uh (Caeltueih 19).  
\ip Paul loh Ephesa rhoek te hingnah thai dongah hing sak a ngaih (4.17—5.20). Pathen hnukbang rhoek neh Pathen ca rhoek tah amah te a tingtawk la hing saeh (5.1). Yinnah neh a hmuep kah khosa rhoek khaw tahae atah khothaih khosae ah kho sa pawn saeh (5.8,9).  
\ip Paul loh yuu neh va kawng, manu napa ka moeiboe, ca na kah moeiboe kawng dongah Khrihca imkhui cako kawng a thui. (5.21—6.9).  
\ip Ephesus capat he AD 60 tluk vaengah a tael.  
\iot Sawt Yoeinah  
